com.avaya.ic.sdk
Interface CategoryGroup

All Superinterfaces:
Code
public interface CategoryGroup
extends Code

Represents a Category Group. Extends Code and exposes all methods on the Code interface. A CategoryGroup provides access to CategoryCodes associated with the CategoryGroup. A CategoryCode provides access to all the ReasonCodes and OutcomeCodes associated with the CategoryCode.
